-- Brazil Will Try to Prevent Real Gains as Europe Recovers, Mantega Says
-- Arnaldo Galvao
-- 2010-06-21T22:53:52Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-21/brazil-will-try-to-prevent-real-gains-as-europe-recovers-mantega-says.html

          
          
             The Brazilian government will seek
to prevent the real, the country’s currency, to gain as a result
of the recovery of the European economy, Finance Minister Guido
Mantega said.  
 “We have tools to prevent that, but there will be
pressure,” Mantega told reporters today in Brasilia.  
